summary: An Ordinance accepting a franchise from King County to maintain and operate watermain pipelines on a portion of Northeast 8th Street between 140th Avenue Northeast and 152nd Avenue Northeast, and also on a portion of J.C. O'Conner's Road between 148th Avenue Southeast and Southeast 16th Street; and authorizing and directing the Mayor and City Comptroller of the City of Seattle to sign said franchise for and on behalf of said City.
